A single class for getting text from lipsum.com (lorem ipsum):

Get a specified number of words:
Lipsum.GetWords(int count);

Get a specified number of paragraphs
Lipsum.GetParagraphs(int count);

Get a specified number of lists
Lipsum.GetLists(int count);


Each method returns a html string containing the requested data.
E.g.

Lipsum.GetWords(5); // could return "<p>\nNunc in tortor in risus.\n</p>"